title: Beautiful updated 3 bed 3 bath townhouse with 1 Bdrm on ground floor!
posting_body: ['Beautiful updated 3 bed 3 bath townhouse with 1 Bdrm on ground floor.', 'Stainless steel appliances with glass tile backsplash.', 'Private fenced courtyard.', 'Security patrol.', "''A'' rated Schools, hammock point elementary school within walking distance.", 'Banyan lakes community offers a pool, gym, sauna, steam room, tennis courts, and playroom for kids.', 'Pet friendly with beautiful lake and walking trail.', 'One assigned parking spot and one guest spot per owner.', 'Located in the heart of Boca Raton, close to shopping, dinning, FAU, minutes to Town Center Mall, Uptown Boca and Mizner park.', 'Must be approved by HOA, which can take up to 30 days.', '$150 application fee, $500 refundable security deposit and $500 non refundable one time rental fee to HOA.', 'First, last, and security deposit required upon mov', 'Contact us to schedule a tour today.', 'Please TEXT me your NAME and', 'AD REFERENCE', 'below and We will contact you ASAP.', 'Book your appointment online today!', 'ANNUAL RENTALS ONLY.', 'Ad Reference:', 'R-10812416', 'Text at:', 'show contact info', 'Ask for ANDREW', 'Availability can change daily, If this rental is not available or isn’t the property for you, Text me or call me and We will help you find the right residence for you.', 'We have rentals all over Palm Beach and Broward County!']
